Introduction

XODIAC a nine-member boy group under One Cool Jacso Entertainment that debuted on April 25, 2023, with the digital single "Throw A Dice".

Prior to their debut, the group was initially known as OCJ NEWBIES, with their pre-debut lineup revealed in May 2022. Over time, some members left, such as Chibin and Austin, the latter pursuing an acting career under the stage name Seunga. XODIAC eventually unveiled their official name and logo in December 2022.
